ef="https://dataportal.orr.gov.uk/statistics/compendia/toc-key-statistics/" target="_blank">https://dataportal.orr.gov.uk/statistics/compendia/toc-key-statistics/</a></p>","Daventry","Chris Heaton-Harris",,"2019-09-09T16:14:05.213Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144413/answer","Biography information for Chris Heaton-Harris","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144413/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144413/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2019-09-03","Train Operating Companies: Staff","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what assessment his Department has made of the proportion of train operating companies’ workforce that is employed by outsourced companies.","false","Biography information for Jo Platt","Leigh","Jo Platt","286376"
